description: This class defines a data transfer object ResultResponse, with fields representing the result details of a machine learning finetuning job, including IDs, model information, and timestamps. It contains getter and setter methods for each field, and uses Swagger annotations for API documentation.

classes.name: ResultResponse
classes.description: A DTO encapsulating finetuning result details including IDs, model info, artifact and metrics paths, and creation timestamp.

methods.name: getJobId
methods.description: Returns the job ID associated with the result.

methods.name: getModelName
methods.description: Returns the name of the base model.

methods.name: getArtifactPath
methods.description: Returns the file path to the result artifact.

methods.name: getMetricsPath
methods.description: Returns the file path to the metrics.

methods.name: getCreatedAt
methods.description: Returns the timestamp of result creation.
